       Megatron cruises to the scene, behinde him are Marine, Pheniox, 
Jackle, Gremlin, and Megaton. He see's the attack...and the Energonians.
       "Ominous Prime? He's returned? This is a rather interesting turn of 
events, yes." Megatron says, as he picks up speed to get a shot at Killfest.
       He see's him throw Aerostreak as if he were a toy...and then blast him 
with two missles. Megatron brought his dino-arm shoulder blasters online, and 
fired at Killfest. "If you want revenge, Killfest, I suggest you get it while 
you can! Yes!"

       Tankkor drives as the two missle burst behinde him, sending him 
stumbling forward a bit. He turns to see the reinforcements have arrived. At 
least it brings a little relief. He raises his arm back at Endbringer, and 
begins to shoot off plasma blast after plasma blast at him.

       Akron is sent flying backward from the shot, but quickly gets up as 
the energy from the shot rushes through her body like a jolt of energy. "Come 
on, big boy. Lets get tough!" She says, and, taking out her energon riffle, 
begins to fire off shots at his face.

       Putnam is hit by Goldeneye, but flies up above her and kicks hard. 
"Give me the vermine! I swear youre going to regreat this...." He says, and 
brandishes a glowing blue fist at the bird.



--part1_ae.f41e061.27836ff5_boundary
